{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"metadata": {"doc_id": "bfba433828f6e5660f97876057d0ac51", "source": "NexaCorp Policy Handbook v5.2", "part": "2. Code of Business Conduct & Ethics", "section": "", "subsection": "", "raw_content": "NexaCorp's reputation for integrity is one of its most valuable and irreplaceable assets. Every employee, contractor, board member, and agent acting on NexaCorp's behalf is expected to uphold the highest ethical standards in every interaction. This Code of Business Conduct & Ethics (the 'Code') establishes minimum standards. Where local law, professional ethics rules, or client contractual requirements impose a higher standard, that higher standard shall apply. IMPORTANT: The Code applies to NexaCorp Global, Inc. and all its wholly-owned subsidiaries, joint ventures where NexaCorp holds a controlling interest, and any individual or entity acting in an authorised capacity on NexaCorp's behalf.", "type": "text"}, "page_content": "Part: 2. Code of Business Conduct & Ethics\n            Section: \n            Subsection: \n            NexaCorp's reputation for integrity is one of its most valuable and irreplaceable assets. Every employee, contractor, board member, and agent acting on NexaCorp's behalf is expected to uphold the highest ethical standards in every interaction. This Code of Business Conduct & Ethics (the 'Code') establishes minimum standards. Where local law, professional ethics rules, or client contractual requirements impose a higher standard, that higher standard shall apply. IMPORTANT: The Code applies to NexaCorp Global, Inc. and all its wholly-owned subsidiaries, joint ventures where NexaCorp holds a controlling interest, and any individual or entity acting in an authorised capacity on NexaCorp's behalf.", "type": "Document"}}